{
  "stem": "2833.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And so the food was brought there and cooked there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we were in there without going out, except if you had a separate permission, because you had some kind of a job that demanded that you walk around in the town from one barrack to the other.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Then it was easy, and you could get out and walk around during the day, at least.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And that's what this lady did for me, whose mother I had helped.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "She became the, what they called barrack's eldest.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Everybody who was in charge of something was always the eldest.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Like in Terezin, the head of the Jewish community-- of the Jewish people-- who-- who ran the ghetto-- was a man of 35 years old.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But he was called Jewish eldest.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, all that-- that happened when we arrived, really, that we were brought into the army barracks.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were some small rooms and some big ones.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And some were 110 people, and some were only 20.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And some were-- I was very lucky.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I got one for my mother, my aunt, and two of their friends, which was a very small room.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I stayed in the next room, which was connected with a few other girls, that we were 12 in one room.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we really had nothing to do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We-- we couldn't go out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I-- after a little while, I did.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But most of the women, like my mother, was for months in there without ever getting out on the street.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there were-- after a little while, we had to work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But at the beginning, there was nothing-- no work, no-- just sit and wait for the day to go by.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was-- in '41, I was 22, yeah.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother was-- I think, 48-- 48 or 49.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
